Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to be followed by 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Time until 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from the start of the case
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for a case to be resolved after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' until case closure
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Time of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in comparison to the average time of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' Cycle Time in comparison to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' Cycle Time
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time to reach 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases leading to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases with 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases with re-submission
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to the end of the process in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER does not occur

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' resolution in cases that also include 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER occurs
